# MyToken Contract

This is a Solidity contract for creating a token called "META"

## Contract Details

Token name is META
Token abbrevation is MTA
Total initial supply is 0

## Mapping Variable
A mapping is use to associate addresses their own token balances. shows the balances of token in the desired address

## Functions
mint function : allows to increase the total supply by the desired value to an address we input
burn function: allows to deduct the token of desired value from the total supply

using if statement for the prevention of burning the tokens that is more than the total supply

